e:T701,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Fotor AI better than Kaiber?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Fotor AI scores 5.0 overall while Kaiber scores 6.0. Fotor AI is best for photo editing and image enhancement, while Kaiber excels for music videos and animations."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Fotor AI or Kaiber?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Fotor AI starts at Free and Kaiber starts at $10/mo. Fotor AI offers a free plan.  Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Fotor AI to Kaiber?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Fotor AI and Kaiber support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Fotor AI vs Kaiber?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Fotor AI holds an overall rating of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10. Kaiber has an overall rating of 6/10 and ease of use score of 7/10. Users praise Fotor AI for combines ai generation with photo editing and Kaiber for unique video and animation generation."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Fotor AI or Kaiber?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Kaiber for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Fotor AI remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize combines ai generation with photo editing. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$e"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-header","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","child