1c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Fotor AI is best suited for photo editing, image enhancement, background removal, quick designs, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Kaiber, meanwhile, shines for music videos, animations, social content, creative videos, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2012, Fotor AI describes itself as \"AI-powered photo editor with image generation and enhancement.\" Kaiber, established in 2022, positions itself as \"AI creative platform for generating animated and video content.\" With 10 years between them, Fotor AI brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Kaiber offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
1d:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Kaiber** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (6.0 vs 5.0). However, this does not mean Fotor AI is a poor choice — far from it. Fotor AI excels in its own right, particularly for photo editing and image enhancement.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value unique video and animation generation, go with Kaiber. If combines ai generation with photo editing matters more to you, Fotor AI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
